negative.review:
Do not recommend this game, as the game developer group is ruining all players game experience

[h2] This may be RUMOUR but makes sense [/h2]

PA is putting all effort into Crimson Desert, but its development is really a burn of money, so——
Black Desert is the blood bag for the new game, the deve group's new work is squeezing the last drop of blood from BDO players;

The old BDO deve group has been promoted(?). they are now working for Crimson Desert, and a new group is in charge of BDO, which explains why recent changes are so toxic as they are entirely new and know little about the game;

(based on former PA Korean staff) Many ART staffs had been fired, maybe this explains why we only have one unique outfit for new chars(especially weapon skins), and just add universal outfits for all chars;

J no longer in charge of BDO anymore, he got promoted, so all his previous promises are now wasted. He used to promise that [b] PA would NEVER NERF any single class, if one was too OP, they would BUFF ALL OTHER CHARS to that level. [/b] But once that two phatty guys came, all players got trolled.

Do not recommend this game, as the game developer group is ruining all players game experience

